snippet: The price to dine with the president was high. But supporters could hear him speak after a concert for $100.
abstract: The price to dine with the president was high. But supporters could hear him speak after a concert for $100.
lead_paragraph: CHICAGO -- Telling supporters that change may be hard but remains possible, President Obama received a warm welcome home here on Wednesday, bolstering his 2012 campaign coffers at three fund-raisers attracting an eclectic mix of wealthy donors and spirited college students.
